text: Ligita Tumāne (born 1 May 1996) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a defender for Italian Serie C club ASD FC Sassari Torres Femminile and the Latvia women's national team. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers Category:Torres Calcio Femminile players Category:Latvian expatriate footballers Category:Latvian expatriate sportspeople in Italy Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Italy Category:Rīgas FS players
